The '''Intersystem Library Exchange''' was a construct of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] that allowed [[Star system/Legends|systems]] to access information from another system's databanks. Several [[Yevetha]]n [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] had once participated in the Exchange. [[Hiram Drayson/Legends|Hiram Drayson]] had a proposal that would revive the Exchange that he wanted to bring forth to the Yevetha.<ref name="BTS">''[[Before the Storm]]''</ref>

